             were indicted for that <rs id="t18130217-21-off127" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18130217-21-off127" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18130217-21-off127" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               they, about the hour of seven in the night, on the <rs id="t18130217-21-cd128" type="crimeDate">26th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130217-21-off127 t18130217-21-cd128"></join>, being in the dwelling-house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130217-21-victim222" type="victimName">
                           William 
